168
00:29:41,630 --> 00:29:42,760
¡Ya veo!

169
00:29:42,760 --> 00:29:45,470
Entonces, basta con...

170
00:29:46,470 --> 00:29:48,350
...patearle el trasero
 a Crocodile, ¿no?

171
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:53,400
Luffy-san...

172
00:30:11,210 --> 00:30:14,670
¡Ha ganado!

173
00:31:28,530 --> 00:31:31,490
No dudes de él, Koza.

174
00:31:37,420 --> 00:31:39,750
La lluvia caerá.

175
00:31:58,520 --> 00:31:59,560
Lluvia...

176
00:32:11,700 --> 00:32:13,200
La locura ha cesado.

177
00:32:14,370 --> 00:32:16,460
Sus armas demuestran duda...

